headline: US oil futures unchanged despite API showing surprise build in US crude stocks
summary: Investing.com -- U.S. crude oil futures were roughly unchanged from post-settlement levels Tuesday despite the American Petroleum Institute reporting a surprise decline in weekly domestic crude inventories.
